@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
```

**‚ùå FORBIDDEN**: Writing custom CSS that duplicates Tailwind utilities
- ‚ùå NO custom `.container`, `.grid`, `.flex` classes
- ‚ùå NO custom responsive breakpoints (use `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`)
- ‚ùå NO custom spacing utilities (use `p-4`, `m-2`, `gap-4`, etc.)
- ‚ùå NO custom color utilities (use `bg-blue-500`, `text-red-600`, etc.)

### 2. Skeleton UI Integration (REQUIRED)
**MUST import Skeleton styles in `src/routes/+layout.svelte`:**
```svelte
<script>
  import '@skeletonlabs/skeleton/styles/skeleton.css';
  import '../app.css';
</script>
```

**MUST configure Skeleton plugin in `tailwind.config.js`:**
```javascript
import { skeleton } from '@skeletonlabs/tw-plugin';

export default {
  content: [
    './src/**/*.{html,js,svelte,ts}',
    require('path').join(require.resolve('@skeletonlabs/skeleton'), '../**/*.{html,js,svelte,ts}')
  ],
  plugins: [skeleton()],
  // ... rest of config
};
```

### 3. Component Styling Rules (MANDATORY)
**‚úÖ ALWAYS USE Skeleton classes for components:**
- Tables: `table table-hover` (NOT custom `.table-financial`)
- Cards: `card` (NOT custom `.card`)
